name: Here Come the Lil' Horrors
description:
4000px x 5079px 300DPI PNG

Here come the Lil Horrors, an intrepid gang of spooks hailing from Salem Dimension 66F who get up to mischief and hijinx. The gang consists of the leader Manny the Sugar Skull, Jackie the Lantern, Blair the Void Witch, Boris the Bandaged, Ludwig the Vegan Vampr and his loyal Battsy, Selina the servant of Bastet, Doc the Victorian lost in time and lastly Chuuum the lost son of an ancient god from beyond and who which the gang must help to bring back to his father.
